{"kanda":6,"sarga":48,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"भर्तारंनिहतंदृष्टवालक्ष्मणंचमहाबलम् ।विललापभृशंसीताकरुणंशोककर्शिता","trans":"On seeing her husband killed and also mighty Lakshmana, Sita became emotional in intense sorrow and cried piteously.","words":[{"d":"सीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"निहतम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"भर्तारम्","m":"husband"},{"d":"महाबलम्","m":"mighty"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणंच","m":"Lakshmana also"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"intense"},{"d":"शोककर्शिता","m":"emotional in sorrow"},{"d":"करुणम्","m":"piteously"},{"d":"विललाप","m":"cried."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"ऊचुर्लक्षणिकायेमांपुत्रिण्यविधवेतिच ।तेऽद्यसर्वेहतेरामेज्ञानिनोऽनृतवादिनः","trans":"\"Whoever was capable of predicting the future have said that I will be the mother of sons and not become a widow. Now if Rama is dead, they become liars.\"","words":[{"d":"ये","m":"whoever"},{"d":"लक्षणिकाः","m":"capable of predicting"},{"d":"माम्","m":"my"},{"d":"पुत्रिणी","m":"mother of sons"},{"d":"अविधवेतिच","m":"not become a widow"},{"d":"ऊचुः","m":"told"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"ज्ञानिनः","m":"knowledgeable, capable of reading future"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"their"},{"d":"रामे","m":"Rama"},{"d":"हते","m":"killed"},{"d":"अनृतवादिनः","m":"liars."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"यज्वनोमहिषींयेमामूचुःपत्नींचसत्त्रिणः ।तेऽद्यसर्वेहतेरामेज्ञानिनोऽनृतवादिनः","trans":"\"Whoever conducted sacrificial ceremonies and are knowledgeable of sastras have told me that I would be consort. They are all liars now as Rama is killed.\"","words":[{"d":"ये","m":"whoever"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"यज्वनः","m":"men who conduct sacrificial ceremonies"},{"d":"महिषीम्","m":"consort"},{"d":"सत्त्रिणः","m":"knowledgeable of sastras"},{"d":"पन्तीम्","m":"with wife"},{"d":"ऊचुः","m":"told"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"तेज्ञानिनः","m":"those wise"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"told"},{"d":"रामे","m":"Rama"},{"d":"हते","m":"is dead"},{"d":"अनृतवादिनः","m":"liars."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"ऊचुस्संश्रवणेयेमांद्विजाःकार्तान्तिकाश्शुभाम् ।तेऽद्यसर्वेहतेरामेज्ञान