ails are round"},{"d":"स्निग्धाः","m":"well proportioned"},{"d":"समाश्च","m":"and bright."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"स्तनौचाविरळौमामकौमग्नचूचुकौ ।मग्नाचोत्सङ्गिनीनाभःपार्श्वोरस्कंचमेचितम्","trans":"\"My breasts are well formed and developed, the nipples are depressed and joined, the navel is deep, and the surrounding part is fleshy.\"","words":[{"d":"मामकौ","m":"my"},{"d":"स्तनौ","m":"breast"},{"d":"अविरळौ","m":"well formed"},{"d":"पीनौ","m":"developed"},{"d":"मग्नचूचुकौ","m":"depressed nipples"},{"d":"उत्सङ्गिनी","m":"joined"},{"d":"नाभिः","m":"navel"},{"d":"मग्ना","m":"deep"},{"d":"मे","m":"my"},{"d":"पार्श्वोरस्कंच","m":"and the surrounding area"},{"d":"चितम्","m":"fleshy."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"ममवर्णोमणिनिभोमृदून्यङ्गरुहाणिच ।प्रतिष्ठितांद्वादशभिर्मामूचुश्शुभलक्षणाम्","trans":"\"My complexion is like the shine of a gem. My hair on the skin is soft. When I touch the ground with my ten fingers and toes, it is said to leave auspicious marks.\"","words":[{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"वर्णः","m":"colour"},{"d":"मणिनिभः","m":"shine of gem"},{"d":"अङ्गरुहाणि","m":"hair on my skin"},{"d":"मृदूनि","m":"soft"},{"d":"द्वादशभिः","m":"ten fingers and toes"},{"d":"प्रतिष्ठिताम्","m":"when placed on the ground"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"शुभलक्षणाम्","m":"auspicious marks"},{"d":"ऊचुः","m":"said to be."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"समग्रयवमच्छ्रिद्रपाणिपादंचवर्णवत् ।मन्दस्मितेत्येवचमांकन्यालाक्षणिनोद्विजाः","trans":"\"My palms and feet placed together have no space which are auspicious marks and brahmins have said that my gentle smile is also a mark of auspiciousness.\"","words":[{"d":"पाणिपादंच","m":"palms and feet"},{"d":"समग्रयवम्","m":"with no space in between"},{"d":"अच्छ्रिद्रम्","m":"collected"},{"d":"वर्णवत्","m":"described"},{"d":"मन्दस्मिता","m":"gentle smile"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"माम्","m":"myself"},{"d":"कन्यालाक्षणिनः","m":"marks of auspiciousness"},{"d":"द्विजाः","m":"brahmins."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"आधिराज्येऽभिषेकोमेब्राह्मणैःपतिनासह ।कृतान्तकुशलैरुक्तंतत्सर्वंवितथीकृतम्","trans"