lling you.\"","words":[{"d":"सा","m":"he"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"सुखोदयैः","m":"the army"},{"d":"अनुमानैः","m":"not doubtful"},{"d":"सविस्रब्धाः","m":"not perturbed"},{"d":"भव","m":"you"},{"d":"अहतौ","m":"not killed"},{"d":"काकुत्स्थौ","m":"Kakutsthas"},{"d":"पश्य","m":"seeing"},{"d":"स्नेहात्","m":"lovingly"},{"d":"एतद्","m":"all this"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"ब्रवीमि","m":"telling."}]},{"v":29,"dev":"अनृतंनोक्तपूर्वंमेनचवक्ष्येकदाचन ।चारित्रसुखशीलत्वात् प्रविष्टाअसिमनःमम","trans":"\"I have not uttered untruth earlier nor shall I do now. Indeed, you have found entry into my mind being a woman of good disposition.\"","words":[{"d":"नउक्तपूर्वम्","m":"not uttered earlier"},{"d":"नचवक्ष्ये","m":"nor tell a lie"},{"d":"कदाचन","m":"indeed"},{"d":"चारित्रसुखशीलत्वात्","m":"woman of good disposition"},{"d":"मम","m":"I am"},{"d":"मनः","m":"heartily"},{"d":"प्रविष्टाअसि","m":"found entry into my mind."}]},{"v":30,"dev":"नेमौशक्यारणेजेतुंसेन्द्रैरपिसुरासुरैः ।तादृशंदर्शनंदृष्टवामयाचावेदितंतव","trans":"\"These two are not capable of being won in war even by gods or demons. On observation of the indications by me I am making you realize.\"","words":[{"d":"इमौ","m":"these"},{"d":"सेन्द्रैः","m":"Indra"},{"d":"सुरासुरैरपि","m":"even Suras or Asuras also"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in war"},{"d":"जेतुम्","m":"to win"},{"d":"नशक्यौ","m":"not capable"},{"d":"तादृशम्","m":"indications of life"},{"d":"दर्शनम्","m":"observation"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"आवेदितुम्","m":"making you to know."}]},{"v":31,"dev":"इदंचसुमहचचित्रंशरैःपश्यस्वमैथिलि ।निस्संज्ञावप्युभावेतौनैवलक्ष्मीर्विमुञ्चति","trans":"\"O Mythili! Even though both of them have fallen and unconscious under arrows their body splendour has not diminished. You may see.\"","words":[{"d":"मैथिलि","m":"Mythili"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"निस्संज्ञावपि","m":"unconscious also"},{"d":"उभौ","m":"both"},{"d":"अपि","m":"indeed"},{"d":"एतौ","m":"these"},{"d":"लक्ष्मीः","m":"prosperous"},{"d":"नैवमुञ्चति","m":"body splendour not diminished"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"सुमहत्","m":"great"},{"d":"चित्रम्","m":"wonder"},{"d":"पश्यस्व","m":"you may see"}]},{"v":32,"dev":"प्रायेणगतसत्त्वानांपुरुषाणांगतायुषाम् ।दृश्यमानेषुवक्त्रेषुपरंभवतिवैकृतम्","trans":"\"Normally when we see men who have ceased life and stopped breathing their features are unappealing.\"","words":[{"d":"प्रायेण","m":"normally"},{"d":"गतायुषाम्","m":"ceased of life"},{"d":"गतसत्त्वानाम्","m":"whose breathing has stopped"},{"d":"पुरुषाणाम्","m":"among men"},{"d":"दृश्यमानेषु","m":"when we see"},{"d":"वक्त्रेषु","m":"in features"},{"d":"परम्","m":"very"},{"d":"वैकृतम्","m":"unappealing"},{"d":"भवति","m":"will be"}]},{"v":33,"dev":"त्यजशोकंचमोहंचदुःखंचजनकात्मजे ।रामलक्ष्मणयोरर्थेनाद्यशक्यमजीवितुम्","trans":"\"O Janaka's daughter! You give up grief and delusion about Rama and Lakshmana. They are alive, no doubt.\"","words":[{"d":"जनकात्मजे","m":"Janaki"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणयोः","m":"Rama and Lakshmana अर्थे both"},{"d":"शोकम्","m":"sorrow"},{"d":"दुःखंच","m":"and grief"},{"d":"मोहंच","m":"and delusion"},{"d":"त्यज","m":"giving up"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"get up"},{"d":"अजीवितुम्","m":"are alive"},{"d":"नशक्यम्","m":"not possible."}]},{"v":34,"dev":"शुत्वातुवचनंतस्याःसीतासुरसुतोपमा ।कृताञ्जलिरुवाचेमामेवमस्त्वितिमैथिलि","trans":"Sita who was like deity, on hearing the words of consolation, spoken by Trijata, greeted Trijata with palms together.","words":[{"d":"सुरसुतोपमा","m":"equal to deities"},{"d":"मैथिली","m":"Mythili"},{"d":"सीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"तस्याः","m":"her"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words of consolation"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"कृताज्ञलिः","m":"greeted with both palms together"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":35,"dev":"विमानंपुष्पकंतत्तुसन्निवर्त्यमनोजवम् ।दीनात्रिजटयासीतालङ्कामेवप्रवेशिता","trans":"Then Trijata took Sita in the Pushpaka chariot endowed with the speed of mind and entered Lanka.","words":[{"d":